---
title: Classic Pork Sausages & Spiced Wedges with Rainbow Apple Slaw
description: It's hard to beat simple and classic. Tasty pork sausages baked in the oven, golden Creole-spiced wedges and a tangy and
refreshing apple slaw is all you need to win hearts all around the dinner table.
